Welcome to Dirty Harry's Daytona Beach
Our History
Dirty Harry's is located in the 700 block of Main Street - the heart of Daytona Beach and home of various festivals and events throughout the year.  We are only a short walk from the Ocean Center and Peabody. Dirty Harry's inside, is a cozy pub  with a Juke Box, Pool Table & More.  Outside, Dirty Harry's transforms its palm tree-lined parking area into a massive block party complete with an outdoor stage for live bands and contests during the larger events.
